      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 8,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 9,
      "text": "Dick Rankin Tells",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 10,
      "text": "Of Odd Aircraft",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 11,
      "status": "blank"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 12,
      "text": "More reports of \"flying flap-",
      "status": "permanent_unresolved",
      "unresolvedReason": "other_documented"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 13,
      "text": "jacks\" turned up Wednesday,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 14,
      "text": "one from no less than Dick",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 15,
      "text": "Rankin, brother of the late Tex",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 16,
      "text": "Rankin, and himself an expe-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 17,
      "text": "rienced pilot of more than 7000",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 18,
      "text": "hours' flying time.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 19,
      "text": "Rankin, who is recovering",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 20,
      "text": "from an old back injury re-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 21,
      "text": "ceived in an automobile acci-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 22,
      "text": "dent, came to Portland over",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 23,
      "text": "the week end to spend the sum-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 24,
      "text": "mer. He saw the \"silver sau-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 25,
      "text": "cers\" over Bakersfield, Cal.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 26,
      "text": "June 23, while lying on the",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 27,
      "text": "lawn sun bathing, he told The",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 28,
      "text": "Oregonian.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 29,
      "text": "\"I hesitated to say much",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 30,
      "text": "about them,\" Rankin said, \"un-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 31,
      "text": "til I noticed all the hullabaloo",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 32,
      "text": "in the papers. I puzzled over",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 33,
      "text": "their strange shape for a while",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 34,
      "text": "and finally concluded that they",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 35,
      "text": "were the navy's new XF5U-1",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 36,
      "text": "flying flapjacks, which are thin",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 37,
      "text": "and round, with twin propellers",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 38,
      "text": "and stubby tail.\"",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 39,
      "text": "Only One XF5U-1 Built",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 40,
      "text": "The navy and the manufac-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 41,
      "text": "turer have announced official-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 42,
      "text": "ly that only one such machine",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 43,
      "text": "was built and that it never left",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 44,
      "text": "Connecticut.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 45,
      "text": "\"These planes were flying",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 46,
      "text": "high, maybe 9000 feet, and fair",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 47,
      "text": "ly fast, about 300 or 400 miles",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 48,
      "text": "an hour. I first counted ten of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 49,
      "text": "them in formation, going north.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 50,
      "text": "About 2:15 P. M. they returned",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 51,
      "text": "on the reverse course, headed",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 52,
      "text": "south. But there were only sev-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 53,
      "text": "en in the formation.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 54,
      "text": "\"They were not weaving or",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 55,
      "text": "bobbing in formation I couldn't",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 56,
      "text": "make out the number or loca-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 57,
      "text": "tion of their propellers and",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 58,
      "text": "couldn't distinguish any wings",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 59,
      "text": "or tail. They appeared almost",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 60,
      "text": "round. They looked like pic-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 61,
      "text": "tures of the navy's flying flap-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 62,
      "text": "jack,\" Rankin said.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 63,
      "text": "Rankin, who plans to spend",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 64,
      "text": "the summer here at 834 N. E.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 65,
      "text": "Simpson street, is now able to",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 66,
      "text": "resume a little flying for fun,",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 67,
      "text": "but not commercially, he said.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 68,
      "text": "He now operates a string of",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 69,
      "text": "auto courts, spending his win-",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
    {
      "lineNumber": 70,
      "text": "ters at Palm Springs.",
      "status": "image_matched"
    },
